snippet.textDisplay: i saw ajr in concert and let me tell you- i was embarrassed. i took no photos, i took no videos, i tried to tell as little people as possible that i was going. my mom really loves them and she loves to go with shows w me so she bought the tickets. we had seen them maybe a year prior at a music festival and honestly it was a fun set! they brought a bit of energy to the stage when we had been getting a little bit bored at that point in the day and we were just waiting for the headliners. but, that was all i needed to hear from them. neotheater came out after the tickets were bought, i avoided listening to it. so come the 2019 concert, i’m hearing all these AWFUL songs for the first time live. and people go crazy for them!!! people love ajr!! we were in the balcony, which was filled with children and when you looked into the pit it was just a sea of those white boys. you could tell that these people thought it was really deep music and i left that show w my head down, hoping no one would see that i went.
